<p>We hate that model, our system is designed to be available when you need us most…After the Sale! We work consistently with owners, managers, etc. to maximize the ROI they see on the BV system. No hidden fees. We do it all: Tech support, consulting on your individual venue, updating prices, recipes, etc., and making sure that you are completely satisfied.</p>
