<p>
BarVision works with as many bar/stations you have in your location. Doesn't matter if your bars are on different floors, inside or outside or in different rooms. BarVision closes the hole on the two big areas of concern in the hospitality market, visibility of liquor pours and real-time inventory control. Shake your money-maker.</p>
